For Arc theme
sudo apt-get install arc-theme
sudo apt-get install chrome-gnome-shell

Open chrome and browse to https://extensions.gnome.org
Enable:
- Dash to Panel
- User themes

Open Tweak Tool (Gnome Tweak Tool)
Set:
Appearance->Themes->Application to Arc-Darker
Appearance->Themes->Shell to Arc-Dark
Desktop->Icons on Desktop->Show Icons off
Fonts->Window Title to Ubuntu Regular size 10
Fonts->Interface to Ubuntu Regular size 10
Extensions->Dash to Panel->Position and Style->Running indicator position to bottom
Extensions->Dash to Panel->Position and Style->Running indicator style (Focused app) to dots
